test olg file for CSVtail stage. 

CSVtail is modified version of CSVstage. 
When receives an input, it reads appended file contents and inject tuples 

To run:

$ ../tests/runOverLog -o csvtail.olg

and then 

$ cat >> testinput
1, 2, 3, 4
